MainGUI
The MainGUI class serves as the primary class to execute the Quine-McCluskey Calculator application.

The QMC Controller class is a JavaFX controller class for the Quine-McCluskey Calculator application.
QuineMcCluskeyCalculator
The QuineMcCluskeyCalculator class provides functionality for simplifying Boolean functions using the Quine-McCluskey (Tabular) Method.
Term
The Term class encapsulates the representation and manipulation of boolean function terms, facilitating the simplification process in the Quine-McCluskey algorithm.
